com.nokia.maps.kml.component

Interface KMLResultSet


  • public interface KMLResultSet
    This interface defines the processed data from a KML Document in the form of MapObjects and details of specified Features.

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      MapContainer getContainer()
      This method retrieves a MapConatiner holding all of the MapObjects parsed from a KML file.
      Feature[] getFeatures()
      This method retrieves all the features associated with this result set.
      KMLMapComponent getKMLMapComponent()
      This method retrieves a KMLMapComponent used for highlighting elements of the result set

    • Method Detail

      • getContainer

        MapContainer getContainer()
        This method retrieves a MapConatiner holding all of the MapObjects parsed from a KML file.
        Returns:

      • getFeatures

        Feature[] getFeatures()
        This method retrieves all the features associated with this result set.
        Returns:
        All of the Feature details from the KML file.

      • getKMLMapComponent

        KMLMapComponent getKMLMapComponent()
        This method retrieves a KMLMapComponent used for highlighting elements of the result set
        Returns:
        A component for highlighting and sending details of the current selected Feature.
